- [ ] **Audience Appropriateness**: Content matches target skill level and interests
- [ ] **Time Alignment**: Realistic timing for all sections and activities
- [ ] **Resource Integration**: All supporting materials properly linked and accessible
- [ ] **Accessibility Compliance**: Meets standards for diverse learners and abilities
- [ ] **Mobile Compatibility**: Readable and functional on different screen sizes

### Training Effectiveness Standards
- **Learning Objectives Achievement**: Content supports stated goals and outcomes
- **Participant Engagement**: Interactive elements and audience participation opportunities
- **Practical Application**: Clear pathways from theory to real-world implementation
- **Knowledge Retention**: Strategies for reinforcing learning and memory
- **Skill Development**: Progressive building of competencies and capabilities

### Technical Validation Standards
- **Cross-Platform Testing**: Verified functionality across different operating systems
- **Media Compatibility**: All audio, video, and interactive elements working properly
- **Link Validation**: All internal and external references functional and current
